{
  "stem": "11089.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you knew then it was ending?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We only heard the shootings, the bombardments of Munich, because we are right beside Munich.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Allach is just beside Munich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and one morning-- I even don't know today how-- it was-- one more day or two, I wouldn't have been survived, because it was the end.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had not what to eat, what to do drink.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're all just-- I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was just climbing on my legs and my hands, and-- And we were sleeping, sleeping.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one morning, we woke-- and I heard the whole night of-- last night was terrible bombardments and shooting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even our barracks was-- we were-- we were shaking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one morning, I woke up, early morning, and I start-- I go out, and I see that the towers of the SS are empty, and little white rags, [NON-ENGLISH] are hanging.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They surrendered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I say to my friend, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, we can go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't-- he couldn't move, he was so-- when I climbed-- I climbed, I didn't have fear anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the first thing was-- I went to the German military camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no Germans anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I climbed in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first thing-- I was smelling, where can I get some food?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm dying!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I smelled and smelled some potato soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went by the smell into a kitchen-- a German kitchen, and I found a big bowl still warm soup.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They left at night, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I put in my head and I was just eating soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thanks God, I didn't kill myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I said, I'm going to go back, but I'm filled with lice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm dirty.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to change my clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went, I-- I found the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
